WEBVTT

00:07.271 --> 00:09.483
Money can change everything:...

00:12.767 --> 00:13.372
...the way you think,...

00:16.183 --> 00:16.527
...act,...

00:18.971 --> 00:20.135
...the way you live.

00:30.456 --> 00:30.780
Come on.

00:31.617 --> 00:32.341
Get out.

00:32.936 --> 00:35.275
It can turn you into someone you barely know,...

00:36.121 --> 00:38.553
...do things you never do,...

00:46.181 --> 00:48.857
...lead you to places you never imagined you'd go,...

00:55.123 --> 00:57.467
Today, a mystery millionaire has saved the children's hospital.

00:57.556 --> 00:59.337
...and choices you never thought you'd make.

00:59.471 --> 01:01.729
...is hailed as a hero for the official opening ceremony.

01:01.921 --> 01:02.433
He's a great man.

01:03.395 --> 01:04.132
Is money good?

01:04.541 --> 01:07.215
Disgraced millionaire plead guilty to corruption charges.

01:07.392 --> 01:08.241
Is money bad?

01:17.175 --> 01:17.803
It's neither.

01:19.698 --> 01:20.644
It's what you do with it.

